<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= canonical %>" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/output.css" />
    <%- include('partials/social-meta') %> <%- include('partials/structured-data') %>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <%- include('partials/header', { active }) %>

    <main class="flex-grow">
      <!-- About page content goes here -->
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">About HomeCleanMN - Your Local Maple Grove Cleaners</h1>

          <div class="mb-8">
            <img src="/images/team-photo.jpg" alt="HomeCleanMN Team providing cleaning services in Maple Grove" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-md mb-4" />
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">Our dedicated team of cleaning professionals serving the NW Metro</p>
          </div>

          <div class="prose max-w-none">
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
              HomeCleanMN was founded in 2010 with a simple mission: to provide exceptional, reliable cleaning services to homes and businesses throughout Maple Grove, Plymouth, Rogers, and the
              surrounding NW metro communities. We're proud to be a local Maple Grove business built on trust and customer satisfaction.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our mission is to create clean, healthy, and comfortable environments for our clients while providing outstanding customer service and employing environmentally friendly cleaning
              practices.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Team</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our team consists of trained and vetted cleaning professionals who take pride in their work. Each member of our staff undergoes rigorous training and background checks to ensure we
              deliver the highest quality service to our clients.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Quality:</strong> We never compromise on the quality of our cleaning services.</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Reliability:</strong> We show up on time, every time, ready to exceed your expectations.</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Honesty:</strong> We operate with transparency and integrity in all our business practices.</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Eco-friendly:</strong> We use environmentally friendly cleaning products wherever possible.</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Customer-centric:</strong> Your satisfaction is our highest priority.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">With so many cleaning services to choose from in the Minneapolis area, why choose HomeCleanMN?</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
              <li class="mb-2">Years of experience serving the local community</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Fully insured and bonded professionals</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Customized cleaning plans to fit your specific needs</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Eco-friendly cleaning options</li>
              <li class="mb-2">Satisfaction guaranteed</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
